#!/usr/bin/env trec
launch

## --------------------------------------------
## ---- Help on how to build ------------------
## --------------------------------------------
type # First we will build and install trec
enter
wait wait
type make clean all
enter wait
type sudo make install
enter wait
wait wait
type # That was it, let's print the help string.
enter
wait wait wait


## --------------------------------------------
## ---- Clean the screen and print help -------
## --------------------------------------------
type clear
enter
wait wait
type trec --help
enter
wait wait


